28
00:01:29,220 --> 00:01:30,140
Believe me.

29
00:01:34,940 --> 00:01:36,020
Believe me!

30
00:02:01,420 --> 00:02:02,220
Okay.

31
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:05,020
I believe you.

32
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:11,500
Remember, Jiang Mohan,

33
00:02:12,740 --> 00:02:13,820
your life

34
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:16,180
is saved by Qinghuan.

35
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:21,020
Retreat.

36
00:02:37,820 --> 00:02:39,020
Very well.

37
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:40,580
you two worked together

38
00:02:41,140 --> 00:02:44,140
just so you could secretly meet
this cursed woman.

39
00:02:44,140 --> 00:02:46,060
This has nothing to do
with the Governor.

40
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:48,140
It was all my idea.

41
00:02:48,780 --> 00:02:50,620
Don't just throw that out without proof.

42
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:52,660
Why don't you watch your man

43
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:54,980
so he'll stop approaching me?

44
00:02:54,980 --> 00:02:56,660
How dare you?

45
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:06,060
I tolerate you

46
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:09,060
because of our cooperation.

47
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:11,100
Don't cross the line.

48
00:03:18,580 --> 00:03:20,380
Speaking of cooperation,

49
00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:23,660
let's have our wedding
the day after tomorrow,

50
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:25,940
or forget the cooperation.

51
00:03:26,540 --> 00:03:28,180
Think carefully about it.

52
00:03:46,220 --> 00:03:47,220
Qinghuan, I...

53
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:48,300
I understand.

54
00:03:53,140 --> 00:03:54,460
You have to do that

55
00:03:54,820 --> 00:03:56,660
to ensure the mission goes smoothly.

56
00:03:58,740 --> 00:03:59,860
Just remember,

57
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:04,660
my body and heart only belong to you.

58
00:04:07,060 --> 00:04:08,780
I know what I'm in for.

59
00:04:09,060 --> 00:04:10,140
Don't worry about me.

60
00:04:19,020 --> 00:04:20,780
What a beautiful starry night.

61
00:04:23,620 --> 00:04:24,940
Let's not think about it.

62
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:26,460
Let's go and see the stars.

63
00:04:27,460 --> 00:04:28,260
Sure.

64
00:04:45,460 --> 00:04:49,180
♪The sky is waiting
for the fog to clear♪

65
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:52,860
♪Like ears waiting for an answer♪

66
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:56,900
♪Those who can't see clearly
still struggle♪

67
00:04:56,900 --> 00:04:58,020
What's on your mind?

68
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:01,140
I'm thinking

69
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:03,940
what it will be like in a hundred years.

70
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:05,820
A hundred years from now,

71
00:05:05,820 --> 00:05:08,100
♪Love hasn't etched itself
into gray hair♪

72
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:10,300
there will be no wars.

73
00:05:11,540 --> 00:05:12,620
The world will be at peace.

74
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:15,380
Everyone will live

75
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:17,420
in a prosperous and peaceful China.

76
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:19,180
♪Whose voice was crawling its way
into my dream♪

77
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:20,140
Sounds wonderful.

78
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:22,460
That means our efforts

79
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:23,980
are worth it.

80
00:05:25,020 --> 00:05:26,580
I wish I could witness that era.

81
00:05:27,220 --> 00:05:30,540
♪Time tells me to let go♪

82
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:31,620
In this life,

83
00:05:31,620 --> 00:05:32,780
♪I've waited for the spring rain
to evaporate in summer♪

84
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:34,140
I owe you too much.

85
00:05:34,740 --> 00:05:37,100
♪And autumn leaves to decay in winter♪

86
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:38,220
If there's a next life,

87
00:05:39,700 --> 00:05:41,540
I only wish to stay by your side.

88
00:05:41,540 --> 00:05:42,940
♪For the flowers we planted together
to bloom in all four seasons♪

89
00:05:42,940 --> 00:05:44,340
I'll give you a peaceful life.

90
00:05:44,620 --> 00:05:46,060
If there is a next life,

91
00:05:46,660 --> 00:05:47,860
I wish to live in a place

92
00:05:47,860 --> 00:05:49,580
with mountains and rivers.

93
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:52,780
♪And the moon and stars to shift♪

94
00:05:52,780 --> 00:05:53,980
I will be a farmer

95
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:56,900
and run a farm of my own.

96
00:05:57,580 --> 00:05:59,900
I'll pick the flowers
that fall in the morning

97
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,300
and enjoy the sunset with you.

98
00:06:02,740 --> 00:06:04,380
I'll be a farmer as well.

99
00:06:05,620 --> 00:06:07,300
We'll build a cottage as our home

100
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:08,740
and make tea in our garden.

101
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:12,340
We'll have a son and a daughter,

102
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:14,540
