105
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:22,980
Do not lose me.

106
00:06:23,780 --> 00:06:25,220
In this life and this world,

107
00:06:25,620 --> 00:06:26,900
in every life to come,

108
00:06:27,300 --> 00:06:28,340
no matter where you are,

109
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:31,900
I will cross the mountains and waters

110
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:34,500
and search through the crowds

111
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:37,220
to reach you.

112
00:06:37,220 --> 00:06:40,180
♪And autumn leaves to decay in winter♪

113
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:43,100
♪But I couldn't wait♪

114
00:06:43,140 --> 00:06:47,820
♪For the flowers we planted together
to bloom in all four seasons♪

115
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:51,700
♪I've waited for the sunset to fall
over mountains and turn into dusk♪

116
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:53,380
If we have a child,

117
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:56,220
what would you name them?

118
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:59,380
If it's a boy, let's call him Jiang Nianzhou.

119
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:01,060
And if it's a girl,

120
00:07:01,780 --> 00:07:02,900
Jiang Nianhuan.

121
00:07:11,300 --> 00:07:12,900
