125
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:28,140
Go.

126
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:30,740
♪A drizzle softly falls
in the deep night♪

127
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:33,180
♪Awakening the jasmine from its slumber♪

128
00:07:34,460 --> 00:07:36,620
♪Two swallows are building
their nest on the beam♪

129
00:07:36,700 --> 00:07:39,860
♪Bringing new mud in their beaks♪

130
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:42,860
♪I gaze into the distance
along the unfamiliar road♪

131
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:46,060
♪Where fragrant grass
is growing lush and thick♪

132
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:50,940
