is nothing without you♪

133
00:07:52,860 --> 00:07:55,260
♪The night wind rises suddenly♪

134
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:58,140
♪Making the pond water ripple♪

135
00:07:58,940 --> 00:08:02,900
♪I fear most when the full moon occurs♪

136
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:05,580
♪We share a smile♪

137
00:08:05,620 --> 00:08:10,140
♪But hide the traces of familiarity♪

138
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:12,620
