141
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:21,900
♪Wishing you would never leave,
staying with me from dawn to dusk♪

142
00:08:21,940 --> 00:08:24,380
♪I never thought we'd part so easily♪

143
00:08:24,460 --> 00:08:27,980
♪While spending forever meeting again♪

144
00:08:28,140 --> 00:08:30,740
♪Why would I not be happy seeing you?♪

145
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:34,860
♪Willow fluff flew around the city
when we met in haste♪

146
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:41,060
♪Falling into a dream,
I can still remember this love♪

147
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:56,620
♪I have tasted all the medicines
in the world♪

148
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:59,940
♪You are the best
that comes with a true heart♪

149
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:02,020
Please put your hands here.

150
00:09:02,660 --> 00:09:06,260
♪My deep love for you
can never heal on its own♪

151
00:09:06,300 --> 00:09:08,700
♪Every time I get closer♪

152
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:11,540
♪My heart flutters
and I let myself get lost in obsession♪

153
00:09:11,540 --> 00:09:13,780
I do not agree to the marriage.

154
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:18,820
