Let go of me!

174
00:10:13,540 --> 00:10:15,260
Chu Yunfan, you jerk!

175
00:10:15,260 --> 00:10:16,540
Let go of me!

176
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:18,780
Let go of me!

177
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:20,780
Put me down!

178
00:10:21,580 --> 00:10:22,820
