179
00:10:22,820 --> 00:10:23,780
Jerk!

180
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:26,380
Disgrace!

181
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:27,700
Sir, I'll get people

182
00:10:27,700 --> 00:10:29,980
to bring your daughter back safely.

183
00:10:31,340 --> 00:10:32,700
What are you waiting for?

184
00:10:33,020 --> 00:10:33,620
Yes, sir.

185
00:10:34,140 --> 00:10:34,860
It's over!

186
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:39,860
It seems the wedding

187
00:10:40,020 --> 00:10:41,820
won't be able to continue.

188
00:10:42,100 --> 00:10:43,300
It's not started yet.

189
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:15,220
♪The wind passes by her without staying♪

190
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:16,180
Am I beautiful?

191
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:18,020
♪Like memories brushing past,
reappearing♪

192
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:21,580
♪Falling like rain through the years♪

193
00:11:21,740 --> 00:11:24,540
♪With eyes wandering,
she searches for a place to belong♪

194
00:11:24,780 --> 00:11:28,100
♪That moment is
like light warming the darkness♪

195
00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:32,020
♪She is my only bond
in the vast sea of people♪

196
00:11:32,300 --> 00:11:35,380
♪I keep leaving and returning♪

197
