out of touch with reality♪

254
00:14:35,940 --> 00:14:38,460
♪I hear the mountains, the seas,
and the people♪

255
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:40,500
♪All clamoring because of you♪

256
00:14:40,620 --> 00:14:42,580
♪Hiding in the cape after the rain♪

257
00:14:42,740 --> 00:14:45,020
♪I cannot hear you♪

258
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:48,540
♪So I opened my arms one last time♪

259
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:52,060
♪But you escaped through the gap♪

260
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:54,380
♪I saw winters come and summers go♪

261
00:14:54,420 --> 00:14:56,540
